{
  "page": "Feature quote/204",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“A daughter. <a href=\"/index.php/Selwyn_Tarth\" title=\"Selwyn Tarth\">He</a> deserves that. A daughter who could sing to him and grace his <a href=\"/index.php/Evenfall_Hall\" title=\"Evenfall Hall\">hall</a> and bear him grandsons. He deserves a son too, a strong and gallant son to bring honor to his name. <a href=\"/index.php/Galladon_Tarth\" title=\"Galladon Tarth\">Galladon</a> drowned when I was four and he was eight, though, and <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Tarth\" title=\"Alysanne Tarth\">Alysanne</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Tarth\" title=\"Arianne Tarth\">Arianne</a> died still in the cradle. I am the only child the gods let him keep. The freakish one, not fit to be a son or daughter.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_31\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 31\">Chapter 31</a>, Brienne VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405130514\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 69/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 309/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/10